com.github.jonathanxd.iutils.map

Class BackedTypedMap<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.jonathanxd.iutils.map.BackedTypedMap<K,V>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TypedMap<K,V>, java.util.Map<K,V>

    public final class BackedTypedMap<K,V>
extends java.lang.Object
implements TypedMap<K,V>
    An TypedMap implementation backed to a provided map, all value types are stored together with values using a Pair. This class may be changed in future to back to BackedTempTypedMap and avoid code duplication.
